She woke up and walked around her room.  She was feeling good and her 
body felt great.  She felt energized and full of life.  The shakes 
came and went time to time, but she was otherwise doining 
wonderfully.  She opened her link,"Hey, Quickstrike, I was wondering 
if there was anything I can do for you or Black Aracnia. I'm doing 
swell and wanted to start being useful around here."
